Package for_Database

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Address
    The Address class represents the address information.
    AddressInfo
    The AddressInfo class represents the contact information consisting of the name and address.
    AddressInfoCollection
    The AddressInfoCollection class links the GUI to the data structures holding the data.
    Database
    The Database applications let's user's enter new contact information into the Database, save the information in the Database to a file, and load the file into the Database.
    Name
    This name class represents the name information.
    UtilityMethods
    The Utility Methods class contains methods to make buttons, textfields, labels, text areas, scroll panes.
